trans-unit.source: Provides a list of XAML nodes, which can be used for scenarios such as writing XAML nodes in a deferred manner.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en liste over XAML nodene, noe som kan brukes til scenarioer for eksempel skriver XAML noder i en utsatt måte.

trans-unit.source: When you create a XamlNodeList, you create a writer delegate that exists as the <xref:System.Xaml.XamlNodeList.Writer%2A> value.
trans-unit.target: Når du oppretter en XamlNodeList, oppretter du en skriver representant finnes som den <xref:System.Xaml.XamlNodeList.Writer%2A>verdi.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlNodeList.Writer%2A>

trans-unit.source: The writer delegate is based on an internal XAML writer class that is specifically for XAML nodes.
trans-unit.target: Representanten writer er basert på en intern XAML writer klassen som er spesielt for XAML noder.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlNodeList"></xref> class, using a provided schema context.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlNodeList"> </xref> class, ved hjelp av en angitt skjema-kontekst.

trans-unit.source: The schema context is applied to the XAML writer that exists as the <xref:System.Xaml.XamlNodeList.Writer%2A> value.
trans-unit.target: XAML-skriveren finnes som gjelder skjemaet konteksten den <xref:System.Xaml.XamlNodeList.Writer%2A>verdi.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlNodeList.Writer%2A>

trans-unit.source: The schema context to use for node operations.

trans-unit.target: Henter antall noder i dette <xref href="System.Xaml.XamlNodeList"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns a XAML reader implementation delegate.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en XAML leser implementering representant.

trans-unit.source: Although it is not specifically a service provider, you can use the <xref:System.Xaml.XamlReader> delegate that is returned from GetReader in a service mode, where you cast it to <xref:System.Xaml.IXamlIndexingReader>.
trans-unit.target: Selv om det ikke er spesielt en leverandør, kan du bruke <xref:System.Xaml.XamlReader>representanten som er returnert fra GetReader i en modus, der du endrer den <xref:System.Xaml.IXamlIndexingReader>.</xref:System.Xaml.IXamlIndexingReader> </xref:System.Xaml.XamlReader>

trans-unit.source: In that mode you can get and set the index values for <xref:System.Xaml.IXamlIndexingReader.CurrentIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: I denne modusen kan du hente og angi indeksverdier for <xref:System.Xaml.IXamlIndexingReader.CurrentIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Xaml.IXamlIndexingReader.CurrentIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: In this manner, the set mode enables skipping nodes without using the standard `Read` and `Skip`.
trans-unit.target: På denne måten Sett modus aktiverer hopper over noder uten å bruke standard `Read` og `Skip`.
